{"tid":582526,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【德國搞成咁】「激嬲老公就會咁！」 敍難民斬死老婆fb直播","createTime":"2018-03-06T09:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T10:08:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":64,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"78b77a7550ec509cb5990f55d88b0970389f1f25","tid":582526,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180306/large/1520304403_fe83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180306%2Flarge%2F1520304403_fe83.jpg&h=1dc1967e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國米赫拉克爾（M&uuml;hlacker）一名敍利亞難民在子女面前捅死分居太太後滿手鮮血之際，竟於社交網Facebook做血淋淋直播，還威脅天下女性：「假如你惹怒了你丈夫，就會落得如此下場。」<br />\n<br />\n41歲的馬爾萬（Abu Marwan）與37歲太太育有兩子一女，一家人都是來自敍利亞的難民，報道指馬爾萬早已不再與妻兒同住，卻經常向太太索錢。<br />\n<br />\n兇案發生在上周五下午4時半左右，馬爾萬在妻兒的家中與太太爭執期間狂捅她的頸，之後帶著其中一名兒子逃亡。馬爾萬在Facebook直播，可見他滿手鮮血，連臉上也沾了血，他說：「我去找我太太，我嘗試解決問題，但她把我趕走，所以我捅了她，用刀捅她，3或4次，她死了或死不了，我不知道。」兩父子更齊齊叫觀眾將片段傳開去，說是給惹怒丈夫的天下女性上一課。<br />\n<br />\n警方指事發時，兩人的年幼女兒在家，是她報警求助。警方出動大批警力四出搜捕，終在案發不久後擒獲馬爾萬。兩人的三名子女，已交由有關機構看管。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180306/57909930\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180306%2F57909930&d=AiK%2FvUy3SAFDSmMwJ3%2B865UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=c75c96c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180306%2F57909930&h=1dbd5dae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180306/57909930</a>"},{"pid":"21e8194777b68cf26784ce37d8b30e96cfb08a5e","tid":582526,"uid":26752,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:05:18.000Z","msg":"叫班左膠情何以堪啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難民vs女權<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgm